## Project Management Rules

### NuGet Package Operations
- MUST use `dotnet add package` command
- Example: `dotnet add package PackageName --version x.x.x | Out-String`

### Solution File Operations
- MUST use `dotnet sln` commands
- Add project: `dotnet sln add path/to/project.csproj | Out-String`
- Remove project: `dotnet sln remove path/to/project.csproj | Out-String`
- List projects: `dotnet sln list | Out-String`

### Project Reference Operations
- Add reference: `dotnet add reference ../OtherProject/OtherProject.csproj | Out-String`
